import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' const UserProfile = () => { const user = useSelector(s => s.user) if (!user) return 'Loading...' return (

Tu perfil:

  • Usuario: {user.name} {user.surname}
  • Email: {user.email}
  • Profesión: {user.profession}
  • País: {user.country}
) } export default UserProfile
